&lt;p&gt;Create a monitoring alert&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id="synopsis"&gt;Synopsis&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Create a new monitoring alert for device conditions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Conditions can be:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;offline: Device becomes unreachable&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;online: Device becomes reachable&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;power&amp;gt;N: Power consumption exceeds N watts&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;temperature&amp;gt;N: Temperature exceeds N degrees&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Actions can be:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;notify: Desktop notification (default)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;webhook:URL: Send HTTP POST to URL&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;command:CMD: Execute shell command&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;



